parameters.name: partner_id
parameters.description: Partner ID is assigned upon registration is successful

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: Used to enforce the freshness of the request. Request will expired after 15 minutes

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: The token for API caller using to identify app permission to our API. Platform admin will provide at token.

parameters.name: shop_id
parameters.description: Shopee's unique identifier for a shop. Required param to call APIs

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: The identifier for an API request for error tracking

notes: The documentation shows both Common Parameters and Response Parameters sections. There are also error codes and example requests/responses shown in JSON format. The API appears to be related to Shopee's platform and deals with checklist agreement attributes.
